1) How do I serve data faster?
        Cache, CDN, Precompute, Fanout
        Feed (Instagram, Twitter, News), Product Listing

2) How do I absorb massive writes safely?
        Queue, Batch, Streaming Processing
        Logging, Analytics-pipeline,Ad click tracking, Web crawler

3) How do I push updates instantly?
        SSE, WebSockets, Pub/Sub, Event streaming
        Chat, Notifications, Live sports updates
        
4) How do I find fast in huge data?
        Indexing(Inverted Index, Trie), Ranking, Cache Hot queries
        Autocomplete, Search engine, 

5) How do I store + deliver large(very large) files efficiently?
        Blob storage, CDN, Async Processing
        YouTube, Instagram-Photos, File upload

6) How do I avoid double spend / race conditions?
        Distributed locks & Transactions, Idempotency keys, Strong consistency design
        Payment system, Ticket booking, Stock trading

7) How do I generate unique, scalable IDs?
        Hashing, Base62 encoding, Snowflake ID generator
        TinyURL, OrderID

8) How do I match nearest entities fast?
      Geohash / quadtrees, Matching engine, Real-time updates
      Uber, Swiggy, Nearby friends





